message.body: Where are you and Hunter these days on the vegan to omnivore spectrum?
I'm eating some seafood/fish and hunter eats almost meat exclusively. Haha. He's going mushrooming tmw in hopes to bring you some!
Let us know what else we can bring!
Do you eat cheese? Can you bring a dessert?
Yes to cheese! I will definitely bring dessert!
Sorry i forgot to get back to you on time for tonight. Is 6ish okay? if you can't make i until later we can also feed the monkey and eat after she goes to bed
